author: COMSOL
description: In this benchmark, a laminated composite shell consisting of eight orthotropic layers with different orientations is subjected to unit loads and a unit change in temperature. The flexibility, stiffness matrices and midplane strains are compared with theoretical and numerical results given in the benchmark.
